### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
### FinanceHQ – Dashboard flow: manual Phase 5 checks
###   5.3 GET /api/dashboard/summary → correct totals for seeded data
###   5.4 GET /api/dashboard/trends?months=3 → 3-item array, ascending order
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Prerequisites:
###   1. Server running on localhost:8080
###   2. Select "dev" environment (top-right in IntelliJ HTTP Client)
###   3. Run auth-flow.http Steps 1–2 first to populate accessToken
###   4. Seed some ONE_OFF transactions first (steps below) then verify dashboard
###   5. Run requests IN ORDER



### ─── SEED: POST ONE_OFF EXPENSE (FOOD $150) — expect 201 ───
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "EXPENSE",
  "category": "FOOD",
  "amount": 150.00,
  "description": "Groceries",
  "date": "2026-06-10"
}


### ─── SEED: POST ONE_OFF EXPENSE (HOUSING $1200) — expect 201 ─
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "EXPENSE",
  "category": "HOUSING",
  "amount": 1200.00,
  "description": "Rent",
  "date": "2026-06-10"
}


### ─── SEED: POST ONE_OFF INCOME (SALARY $5000) — expect 201 ──
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "INCOME",
  "category": "SALARY",
  "amount": 5000.00,
  "description": "Monthly salary",
  "date": "2026-06-10"
}


### ─── SEED: POST RECURRING INCOME — expect 201, must NOT appear in summary totals ─
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "INCOME",
  "category": "SALARY",
  "amount": 9999.00,
  "period": "RECURRING",
  "paymentDay": 25
}


### ─── 5.3: GET summary (current month) — expect:
###   totalExpenses=1350.00, totalIncome=5000.00, netBalance=3650.00
###   expensesByCategory: [{FOOD, 150.00, 1}, {HOUSING, 1200.00, 1}]
###   recurring entry does NOT appear in totals ───────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### ─── 5.3b: GET summary with explicit month param ───────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/summary?month=2026-06
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### ─── 5.3c: GET summary for a past month (expect zeros if no data) ─
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/summary?month=2025-01
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### ─── 5.4: GET trends (3 months) — expect:
###   3-item array in ascending month order (e.g. 2026-04, 2026-05, 2026-06)
###   current month totals match summary above ──────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/trends?months=3
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### ─── GET trends (1 month) — expect 1-item array, current month only ─
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/trends?months=1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### ─── GET trends (default=6 months) — expect 6-item array ────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/trends
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### ─── AUTH BOUNDARY: GET summary without token — expect 401 ───────
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/summary
